{"tid":1016830,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[食盡兩家茶飯] 劉業強:丁權案不動搖新界人愛國愛港信念","createTime":"2019-02-11T04:27:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T18:08:00.000Z","uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e68d4658819bdf35b63c4e0cb04e72dbb8002875","tid":1016830,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:27:45.000Z","msg":"鄉議局主席劉業強在鄉議局新春團拜致詞時表示，香港有一小撮人決意與新界人抬槓，就丁權進行司法覆核，挑戰《基本法》權威和第40條所賦予原居民的合法權益，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但無論案件結果如何，都絲毫不會動搖新界人愛國愛港愛鄉的信念，也不會割斷他們對國家的忠誠</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n劉業強提到，雖然對特區政府某些施政缺失有怨言、不滿和不同意的地方，但充分理解當家的難處，因為世上沒有一個政府是百分百完美，又形容政治是「順得哥情失嫂意」。他續稱，只要當局以「以民為本、依法治港」作為香港管治的大前題，在自己主持下的鄉議局，必然是特首和領導班子的堅強後盾，以及忠誠和可信賴的朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一邊食住英國佬留低政策，一邊講愛國食埋鄰國福利，仲撚衰過以前班漢奸走狗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f7df724b6d84258c7f1f94b03d4e82af79e2ae","tid":1016830,"uid":152476,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T04:34:36.000Z","msg":"愛國<br />\n中共最叻打土豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47b12f8560f04e6964800dc2e3dd9666f29487fb","tid":1016830,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:13:48.000Z","msg":"樂不思蜀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b79afca28044d3694efa2209cd474fb4c54835a9","tid":1016830,"uid":229549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:16:53.000Z","msg":"車公教落要上下同心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0036f39ea587e69d87935522c0810f96fdef1bc1","tid":1016830,"uid":196735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"講都幾動聽"},{"pid":"70c9f074bc451bf0bee491919d64ca68833a8565","tid":1016830,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T05:26:06.000Z","msg":"佢個死鬼老竇擦鞋都無擦得咁明顯<br />\n成個公公咁<br />\n影撚衰d 牛屎佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75c1a6776899d1e74ca475f301c47a6ddc7bee3","tid":1016830,"uid":41394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽講個丁屋政策係港英政府搞出黎  <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d65705e5df7b1d50def838820eb86efa61d17caa","tid":1016830,"uid":53811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T17:28:26.000Z","msg":"終於知道自己企錯邊<br />\n忠誠的人係唔會強調自己忠誠架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69eefe326e288b8d755cc38cc41fe92a8908c67f","tid":1016830,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"全面取消丁權啦"}]}